_ww-text_text.en: Built on the principles of Apple Design, QreamUI Kit delivers a seamless, user-friendly experience tailored to meet the needs of both designers and developers.

Our sizing and spacings primitive, guided by Apple Design standards, ensure consistent and proportional spacing and sizing across all elements and layouts. It facilitates a refined, professional look for your designs.

Our borders and shadows primitive allows for the addition and customization of border shapes and shadow effects. This enhances the appeal of your design elements and aligns with Apple Design standards for visual depth and distinction.

Based on Apple Design Guidelines, our color primitive provides a foundational, yet highly customizable color palette. Its consistency and adaptability contribute to a visually pleasing and uniform design.

Our typography primitive offers a diverse menu of fonts and text styles, crafted in line with Apple Design Guidelines. It ensures text across all elements is legible, appealing, and harmonious with the overall design aesthetic.

Our UI kit effectively leverages WeWeb’s exclusive feature known as Classes. This feature allows designers to define a set of stylistic attributes and apply them across multiple elements, enabling more consistency and speed during the design process. Furthermore, with the use of subclasses, you can easily create and manage variant styles from the base class, allowing for more flexible and diversified design.
